  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个工业物联网系统的时序图，展示从外部Client访问到我们后端服务的完整链路。核心是要体现多层代理结构：Client先打到LoadBalancer，然后到NGINX做路由，最后落到Webservice。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "NGINX",
        "Webservice"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到NGINX层需要做路由决策，这个是要用loop来表示吗？还有，LoadBalancer到NGINX、以及NGINX到Webservice的协议，都是HTTP还是HTTPS？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "NGINX",
        "loop",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "Webservice",
        "HTTPS",
        "HTTP"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，NGINX内部有个route循环来做基于Host的路由选择。协议方面，Client到LoadBalancer是HTTPS，但内部为了性能，LoadBalancer到NGINX以及后续都是HTTP。不过为了可观测性，我们在HTTP头里会打上业务标识，比如IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker、IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic这些。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "HTTPS",
        "NGINX",
        "HTTP",
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "route",
        "loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主链路：Client发起HTTPS GET请求到LoadBalancer，LoadBalancer转发HTTP GET到NGINX，NGINX经过route循环后转发到Webservice。返回路径我也画上，Webservice响应后逐层返回。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Client",
        "LoadBalancer",
        "NGINX",
        "Webservice",
        "HTTPS GET",
        "HTTP GET",
        "route",
        "loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "返回的数据里要体现状态码，Webservice可能返回302或者200。另外返回的时候每一层都要带上对应的业务标识，比如NGINX回LoadBalancer是IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController，LoadBalancer最终回Client是IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Webservice",
        "HTTP 302",
        "HTTP 200",
